HEADWORD: Assignor
<hw>As`sign*or"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>assignator</ets>. Cf. <er>Assigner</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>An assigner; a person who assigns or transfers an interest; <as>as,
the <ex>assignor</ex> of a debt or other chose in action</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

